window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Caina Amalas is a Ghost nightfigher, a spy, and an agent of the emperor, and time and time again she has overcome mighty foes through boldness and cunning.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>But even her boldness might not be enough to stop the coming destruction.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>A secretive cabal of sorcerers has created a weapon so powerful that its wielder will have dominion over the entire world - and the weapon is for sale to the highest bidder.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>Unless Caina unravels the sorcerers' secrets, uncounted millions will perish in the weapon's wrath. Starting with her....</p>"; 
